plucs (0.2-0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Closes #2567: Compatibility with UCS 4.x: new eJabberD version, no
    need for plucs-msrl (msrl module is now a mainstream module shipped
    with eJabberD)
  * Closes #2527: Default of 'xmpp enabled' for new users is now 'true'
  * Closes #2527: Default of 'xmpp domain' for new users will now be
    changed to the first (or only) XMPP domain hosted in this UCS
    domain.

